Question: Do you see either any snowboarders or skateboarders that are jumping?

BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='snowboarder')
IMAGE0=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='skateboarder')
IMAGE1=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX1)
ANSWER0=VQA(image=IMAGE0,question='Is the snowboarder jumping?')

ANSWER2=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} == 'yes' or {ANSWER1} == 'yes' else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
